{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And in Strasbourg, he was going to call us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And the signal was that he would call and say to my mother happy birthday, and he was sorry that he could not get a cake for her in time for her birthday.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "The interesting thing was he left on August 13, and her birthday was actually 10 days later, August 23rd.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "So this was very reasonable for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "The not being able to get the cake would mean that he got the money through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And that was the signal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We waited with a heavy heart, until we stood near-- we stayed near that telephone, and when he hit Strasbourg, and he was across the border, he called us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And then we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "We had packed already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We were leaving the next day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "The family saw us off at the train station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We took with us really our-- just our belongings because we didn't know, you know, like clothing, that's about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Because we didn't know where we were going to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "We went to Strasbourg and we stayed there for about a week and we played tourists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "My dad was a very unusual kind of man, made the decision where we were going to go from there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It was-- it was really very unusual.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "I remember that day, we were in the hotel, he spread out the map.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "He looked at the map, and he said, well, let's not go to Paris, which would have been logical.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Most refugees would go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And for this particular reason, he felt we shouldn't go there because we wouldn't be able to make a living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "There were so many refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "They were overrunning the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And he said, well, let's not go up to Bordeaux, because that-- there's nothing commercial there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
